SUMMARY:HBG - West Shore / Harrisburg Board Gaming - Westshore Edition 
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nCome to game night in Mechanicsburg! Eve
 ry 1st and 3rd Fridays of the month there will be gaming at Wegmans. The e
 vent starts at 6:00 pm and will be in the cafe area and will run until the
  venue closing at 11:00 pm.\n\nPlease be respectful of the venue and limit
  outside food and drink. Would prefer that food and drink be purchased fro
 m the venue as a way of thanking them for providing the space. Come check 
 us out!\n\nJeff Dillman is the organizer of this event\, so message him on
  the Meetup App with any questions.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/centralpagameclub/events/308160869/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250530T160147Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250530T160147Z
